1189
00:53:04,765 --> 00:53:07,184
That's how big a nerd you were.

1190
00:53:07,267 --> 00:53:09,978
But then we realized
Bill knows that much about everything.

1191
00:53:10,062 --> 00:53:11,862
One of the other things
