1193
00:53:14,525 --> 00:53:16,527
But in addition to doing voice work,

1194
00:53:16,610 --> 00:53:18,696
we were able to con you
into doing some writing.

1195
00:53:18,779 --> 00:53:21,174
<i>You didn't have to con me at all.
