1196
00:53:21,198 --> 00:53:23,951
<i>I go, "I can write in a Pixar movie? Yes!"</i>

1197
00:53:24,034 --> 00:53:25,786
All right.

1198
00:53:26,328 --> 00:53:29,415
<i>Just to see the process too,
