1242
00:55:17,356 --> 00:55:20,484
<i>"I'm more worried about the young girl
out in the elements"</i>

1243
00:55:20,567 --> 00:55:22,295
"<i>lying unconscious in the woods.</i>"

1244
00:55:22,319 --> 00:55:25,359
<i>"I don't know if anybody's gonna really
