1246
00:55:29,493 --> 00:55:31,495
<i>I remember that went out the window.</i>

1247
00:55:31,578 --> 00:55:34,665
<i>It was so cool for me
to be able to get a sequence,</i>

1248
00:55:34,748 --> 00:55:36,208
<i>then we would talk it through.</i>

1249
00:55:36,291 --> 00:55:40,087
<i>And then having Cooley there
who also has such a great story brain,</i>

1250
00:55:40,170 --> 00:55:41,797
<i>and Ronnie does... You guys all do.</i>

1251
00:55:41,880 --> 00:55:43,423
<i>I can't draw to save my life.</i>

1252
00:55:43,507 --> 00:55:46,176
<i>But just how quickly
they put up boards.</i>

1253
00:55:46,260 --> 00:55:49,263
<i>Just the immediacy
